videoSnippet.title: Ivanchuk Squeezes Wei Yi in the Rapids to Win the Match (Hoogeveen 2017)
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator A six-game match between experienced Ukrainian super-GM Vassily Ivanchuk and upcoming Chinese talent Wei Yi is played in Hoogeveen, the Netherlands, between October 21 and October 26, 2017. Part of the 21st Hoogeveen Schaaktoernooi, the match is held concurrently with Van Foreest - Adhiban (2017) and three open Swiss System tournaments.

Wei Yi vs Vassily Ivanchuk 
Ivanchuk - Wei Yi (2017), Hoogeveen NED, rd 8, Oct-26 
Scandinavian Defense (B01) 

1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qa5 4. d4 c6 5. Bd2 Bf5 6. Bc4 e6 7. Qf3 Nd7 8. O-O-O Ngf6 9. Nge2 Qc7 10. h3 h6 11. Rhe1 O-O-O 12. Kb1 Bd6 13. g4 Bh7 14. Nf4 e5 15. dxe5 Nxe5 16. Qe2 Rhe8 17. Be3 Nxc4 18. Qxc4 b5
